dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.systemtemplate.transportprotocols

Interface ISomeipTpConnection

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity

    public interface ISomeipTpConnection
extends IEntity
    ISomeipTpConnection: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    A connection identifies the sender and the receiver of this particular communication. The SOME/IP TP module routes a Pdu through this connection.
